snippet.title: 7 Billion Humans - Official Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Automate swarms of office workers to solve puzzles inside your very own parallel computer made of people. ...a thrilling followup to the award winning Human Resource Machine. Now with more humans! COMING SOON!

https://tomorrowcorporation.com/7billionhumans

"TRAVEL WISE"

WITH ROSS HUGUET AS THE ANNOUNCER
